## Memory directories

> Filesystem locations where Claude Code memory files live (`feedback_*.md`,
> `project_*.md`, `reference_*.md`). SpecSwarm scans these during `/ss:init` to
> propose constitution principles auto-generated from existing memory. Listing
> directories here also lets `/ss:specify` and `/ss:clarify` surface relevant
> memory entries when they apply to the current feature.
>
> List directory paths (NOT individual files). Tilde expansion supported.

<!-- Examples (delete or replace):
- path: ~/.claude/projects/-home-user-code-projects-this-project/memory/
- path: ~/.claude/memory/
-->
